s (summoned).<br>
<br>
60 Pally joins the group and we make him MT.  Same mobs, same pulls, same haste.  He is pulling with stun and using Windblade.  Mobs never hit the chanter (10 pct of the time maybe).  <br>
<br>
I have heard others complimenting how mobs stick like glue on pallys.  What's up with that?  Or to put it another way, why would ANYONE ever want a War over a Pally in an XP group?<br>
